    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver or a great project for someone looking to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear quarter panel, and some fading on the clear coat in spots. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, though all major electronics are still functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need a tune-up and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car at an honest price for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
