      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless shape\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
